oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Gentlemen of the Road Series - Lewes Stopover

oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color window card (navy on yellow and light blue) announcing the Gentlemen of the Road Lewes Stopover on July 19-20 with a line up of artists including Mumford and Sons, Edward Sharpe, the Vaccines, the Vampire Weekend, British Sea Power, Edward Sharpe, the Mystery Jets, White Denim, Johnny Flynn and the Sussex, Deep Vally, Youth Lagoon, and Bear's Den.
